/Read Bar 沉静阅读设计/

# Subagent-driven-development scratch ledger
.superpowers/

# Background-sound audio binaries are ignored by default (keep repo light +
# under GitHub's 100MB/file limit). Big source files stay local-only.
# To SHIP a loop on the deployed site, add an explicit exception below for it
# (a small, web-friendly file — a few tens of MB max), like calm-piano.mp3.
*.mp3
*.m4a
*.ogg
*.wav
*.flac

# Shipped background loops (exceptions — these ARE deployed):
# Global shared audio lives at the repo-root /audio/ folder (every book's reader
# page references ../../audio/).
!audio/calm-piano.mp3

